     P2 of the HomeActivity Compose migration: the former second child of the SlidingUpPanelLayout
     (the arrivals panel container). It is now hosted as the `sheetContent` of a Compose
     BottomSheetScaffold; the Compose ArrivalsPanelFragment is added into it programmatically
     (replace R.id.slidingFragment), exactly as before.
-->
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
              android:layout_width="match_parent"
              android:layout_height="match_parent"
              android:clickable="true"
              android:focusable="false"
              android:id="@+id/slidingFragment"
              android:background="@color/trip_details_background"
              android:orientation="vertical">
    <!-- Fragment is added here programmatically -->
</LinearLayout>
